             <div id="question1-btn" class="question-box">
                <h3>What kind of game is Pogiee?</h3>
             </div>
             <div id="answer1-box" class="answer-box">
                 <p>Pogiee is a spelling training tool in the form of a game. We created this tool because we believe in the power of practice.
                   The more you play pogiee, the more you'll notice your spelling improving. For the best results, Once you've conquered easy mode
                   and normal mode. Challenge yourself with hard mode.</p>
             </div>

             <div id="question2-btn" class="question-box">
                <h3>Will Pogiee continue to improve?</h3>
             </div>

             <div id="answer2-box" class="answer-box">
                 <p>Yes Pogiee is very new and will continuously be improving. We will be improving the point system,
                    adding badges and achievements, as well as improving and adding new features. We will also be considering
                    user feed back.</p>
             </div>

             <div id="question3-btn" class="question-box">
                <h3>Will there be new games coming soon?</h3>
             </div>

             <div id="answer3-box" class="answer-box">
                 <p>Yes Pogiee will be adding new games soon. We are focused on creating new games focused on educational training.</p>
             </div>

             <div id="question4-btn" class="question-box">
                <h3>How dose Pogiee improve my spelling?</h3>
             </div>

             <div id="answer4-box" class="answer-box">
                 <p>The more you practice something the better you'll get it. Pogiee makes it easier and more convenient to practice your spelling.</p>
             </div>

             <div id="question5-btn" class="question-box">
                <h3>How can i cancel my subscription?</h3>
             </div>

             <div id="answer5-box" class="answer-box">
                 <p>To cancel your account first you will have to go to your Profile page. then click on account settings. Once your on the
                    account page click on cancel subscription. If you have any further issues contact support by visting the support page.</p>
             </div>

             <div id="question6-btn" class="question-box">
                <h3>How can i reactivate my subscription?</h3>
             </div>

             <div id="answer6-box" class="answer-box">
                 <p>To reactivate your account first you will have to go to your Profile page. then click on account settings. Once your on the
                    account page click on reactivate subscription. If you have any further issues contact support by visting the support page.</p>
